👩‍💼 HR Analytics Dashboard

📌 Project Overview

The HR Analytics Dashboard was designed to analyze employee data and provide actionable insights into workforce trends. It helps HR professionals and business leaders understand employee satisfaction, attrition, and engagement while identifying areas that require strategic improvements.

🎯 Objectives

Track employee satisfaction levels and highlight factors influencing turnover.

Identify at-risk employees who are more likely to leave the organization.

Compare satisfied vs. unsatisfied employees across departments and job roles.

Provide an interactive dashboard for HR teams to make data-driven decisions.

🛠 Tools & Technologies

Excel → for data cleaning and preprocessing.

Tableau → for building interactive dashboards and visualizations.

📊 Key Insights from the Dashboard

Departments with higher workloads showed a higher attrition rate.

Employees with lower satisfaction scores were more likely to leave within a year.

Clear patterns between employee tenure and retention were identified.

The dashboard allows filtering by department, job role, and satisfaction level for deep analysis.

