🚀 How to Use

Clone this repository.

Review the data preprocessing steps (Excel/SQL).

Open the Tableau workbook to interact with the dashboard.

Use filters to explore insights by department, job role, or satisfaction level.

📌 Conclusion

The HR Analytics Dashboard empowers HR teams to improve retention strategies, enhance employee satisfaction, and make data-driven workforce decisions.
